'''Wilam Olgreen''' was an [[Outlaw tech/Legends|outlaw tech]] and droid's rights activist who operated in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]]. He had no permanent base of operations and was frequently on the run from Imperial authorities, but was known to frequent ''[[Omze's Incredible Traveling Starport/Legends|Omze's Incredible Traveling Starport]]'' on occasion. Olgreen's philosophy was that he could best advance the cause of droid's rights by enhancing them and improving on their design and boosting their [[Artificial intelligence/Legends|artificial intelligence]]. Enterprising rogue droids and fellow activists often sought out Olgreen for illegal droid modifications. He was also willing to work on commission, but his prices were steep.

